entries.femaleVariant: Need a smoke. Where'd you stash yours?
Gotta get out of here, understand?
And I'll kill anyone who gets in my way. You included.
How did you get here?
I don't smoke.
Then go out and get some. Just need one last one!
Jesus fucking Christ, man!
The fuck kinda joytoy are you s'posed to be?
Who you work for? Start talkin'!
Fuck!
Fuck!
Fucking chip...
See you never, asshole.
[Take meds]
Don't smoke.
Where'd you even come from?
Not something to focus on, V. Let it go. Here, got some meds for you.
Here, got one more thing for ya.
Vik pulled this outta your skull – a lucky charm?
He was my best friend.
Jack... was the best friend I ever had. I'm 'onna miss him something awful.
If he was here, he'd tell you to get your ass out of bed in the morning and do what you need to do.
He talked about you, lots.
He talked about you, like, lots.
We got into a fight... right before he went off to do this job.
He wa'n't mad at you. I hope you know that.
I know. I just wish our last moments together could've been... different.
[Lie down] I'm exhausted.
Givin' me pills' that'll kill me?
You're lovely, Misty. Thanks.
Misty, wait. Umm... about Jackie...
G'night, V. Sweet, peaceful dreams.
Yeah?
And then he died… and I thought I was gonna die... with him, in my sleep.
Can't actually tell if I'm awake now. I mean, I could be dead already, right?
You're lovely.
About Jackie...
Didn't you hear? My condition's terminal. What good can this do?
Givin' me a pill to prod that sonofabitch? So he can kill me faster?
Your psyche's gonna die, V. You'll feel... your old self slipping away. At some point, you won't recognize yourself.
It'll be terrifying. It'll be painful. But it doesn't have to be.
But right now you need rest. So sleep, please sleep.
How the fuck should I know?
How're we even talking?
I can feel it... our minds... touching...
Don't be silly. As long as you're alive, there's hope. And don't let anyone tell you otherwise.
Really think I can make it, survive this?
'Course you can. I mean, you did already die and come back once, didn't ya?
Helloooooo Night City!
Smack-dab between two Californ-I-As, it's prime real estate, baby, and boy are we open for business!
Your man Stan here! Smog reports comin' in ten times the usual. But my, my, what a gorgeous day this is!
[Take meds]
Ugh. Fuck me...
Rip the thing out myself!
No! Wait!
Ugh...
I'd puke if I fuckin' could!
I'm like mold on fruit... creepin' into you… nothing I can do about it.
You hear me?!
I'm gonna kill you.
Get out of my head.
I'm... gonna kill you.
Leave me alone!
Do it, what're you waiting for?!
Get out! Just get the fuck out!
Not like that!
Stick some iron in your mouth and pull the trigger.
If Watson's the place you haunt, you borged up ghouls, I got good news – cop cordon 'round your 'hood's packed up an' left.
So you peeps open up and let it all hang out today. Could catch a break, start in on a new chapter, a new book, a new life!
Now let's hear what the Rubicones have to say about it! Hit it!
So leave last night's blue dreams and screams in bed, take that first sip of joe with a hot splash of sunshine and seize the day in Night City!
Fuck, fuck, fuck, fuckin' fuck…
It's just a copy of the engram – I'm out there somewhere, gotta be…
Lead to the head. Only thing that'll fix this.
Hear me, bitch?! A bullet to the fucking brain!
entries.maleVariant: Hear me, asshole?! A bullet to the fucking brain!

entries.femaleVariant: Listen, you're likely to be fine for a while. But some time down the road, it could turn into pure agony. I'm givin' you options, honey.
The brain can be tricked. Plain old painkillers do that.
The fuck I need pills for? Oughta just stick a gun in my mouth, pull the trigger.
Well, that way you'd kill two souls. Is that what you want?
I'm so fucking sorry he's gone.
I'm so fucking sorry Jack's not here anymore.
Jackie was special. Really spiritually rich. He touched so many people with his love. Don't worry, he'll be around.
Sure you'll be all right?
I'll be fine. Life is so beautifully powerful, so much more powerful than death.
[Get up]
Omega blockers – taken regularly, they'll keep things from progressing too quickly.
Also, they should keep that guest of yours calm, quiet.
Pseudoendotrizine's from me. Effect'll be opposite. It'll speed things up, free the demon, so to speak.
Gotta lie down…
Promise you'll try to get some sleep?
Got a terminal case of bad luck.
Sleep's a... Small hint of death, the inevitable.
[Sleep]
[Stand]
Fuckin' ghost off!
I'll take control.
I'll FIND a way!
You hear me?!
